data.description: Outstanding home w/ FINISHED BSMNT located in convenient quiet neighborhood! Move right in...LOADS of UPDATES for today's modern living! Terrific floor plan offers oversized Living Rm, Dining Rm, which could be a Flex Rm, Eat in Kitchen overlooking Family Rm w/Wood burning Fireplace for those cool and cozy Fall nights. Awesome FINISHED BSMNT has Media/ Rec Rm and separate office w/ lots of shelves!  Huge Laundry Rm w/ laundry chute, Utility sink and Lots of Storage! You will LOVE the AMAZING FULLY FENCED Backyard for hosting BBQ's and entertaining! YES, Please!!!  Better Hurry on this Beautiful....HOME SWEET HOME!
